&lt;p&gt;We will look to you to bring unexpected, deeply resonant thinking to how we market our journalism, championing creative ideas that can break through the noise of the modern media landscape.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a temporary hybrid role based in our New York City headquarters, reporting to the the Managing Director of Marketing Operations. You can typically expect to come into the office 3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
