&lt;p&gt;You will manage campaign activation, development, optimization and reporting. You will work with internal partners in Marketing, Creative, Data Insights, and Audience in helping us reach our goal to achieve 15 million subscribers by 2027. This is a hybrid role based in our New York headquarters, reporting to the Manager, Growth Media Strategy. You can typically expect to be in the office 3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
