&lt;li&gt;Analyze the data that undergirds these stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop stories that include a wide range of voices and perspectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other members of the Upshot desk and other parts of the newsroom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the accuracy and clarity of the material you publish&lt;/li&gt;
